<plot>Jessica Cavallo is an L.A. police detective investigating a series of killings of lesbian couples where some of the evidence points to a security designer named Eugene Barrows. Jessica's mother, a superior court judge campaigning for city councilperson, advices Jessica to lay off the case for it might hurt her political career. As the killings continue, Jessica cannot get any real evidence against Barrows to arrest him and finds herself suspended from the force, and nobody will believe her suspicions, except for an ambitious female district attorney, named Alex Hanson, whom is following the case. Realizing that Barrows uses his security system to spy on people, Jessica takes drastic steps to lure him into the open by pushing the laws of ethics: by seducing Alex.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?266711</url></doc>
